messages.title: NO TO A SECOND REFERENDUM YES TO A REAL BREXIT
messages.content: This is a Brexit General Election. Our priority is to stop a Corbyn-led Remainer alliance sneaking into power and using a rigged second referendum to overturn the votes of 17.4m Leavers. That’s why we are fighting to win Labour and Remainer-held seats, such as yours.

mentions.tacticalSituation: The Brexit party can beat Corbyn's Labour and take on the Remain alliance – as we proved when we won the May European elections. By contrast, in many Leave-voting Labour seats, the Tories have never won and can’t win this time.

issues.brexitEurope: Our priority is to stop a Corbyn-led Remainer alliance sneaking into power and using a rigged second referendum to overturn the votes of 17.4m Leavers. That’s why we are fighting to win Labour and Remainer-held seats, such as yours.
issues.governance: Parliament’s betrayal of our vote proves that the political system is broken. We need big democratic reforms to make Parliament serve the People.

images.caption: Nigel Farage MEP, Leader of The Brexit Party
